<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div class="container">
<div class="header">
<h1>Account Creation Confirmation</h1>
</div>

<p>Dear {{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

<p>We are pleased to inform you that your account has been successfully created. Complete your signup using the link below.</p>
<a class="button" href="{{{Account.Link}}}">Signup to get started!</a>

<p>Thank you for being a valued member of our community.</p>

<div class="footer">
<p>Best regards,<br />
{{{Organization.Name}}}<br />
Phone: {{{Organization.Phone}}}</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>